About this item

  • 【Materials & Multi-Pocket】Lightweight cargo shorts are made of breathable fabric, features moisture wicking and quick drying, keep you comfortable and cool in summer outdoor activities. The back pocket and the thigh pocket are convenient for storing the items needed for outdoor hiking and leisure work
  • 【D-RING with SMALL POCKET】D-Ring provides easy hook-on installation of hiking gear, which placed in the small pocket and makes it stored stable and safely
  • 【Correct Fit】Classic hiking cargo shorts design button closure with zip fly. A flexible waist creates a more flexible personalized fitting feeling. Flat seams reduce friction for extra comfort and a relaxed exercise experience
  • 【Sun Protection】UPF50 fabric blocks harmful UV rays, provides excellent protection against sunburn. Added durable water repellent finish to repel light moisture and dirt. Great for outdoor hiking and summer travel
  • 【Versatile Occasions】 These outdoor shorts are perfect for golf, travel, hiking, walking

Product Description

The Men's Hiking Cargo Shorts are crafted of lightweight,quick dry and breathable fabric wicks away sweat from your skin,which helps you keep cool and fresh in the hot summer.

Fabric Features

  • The fabric is made of 92% polyester and 8% spandex, which is super stretchy and comfy.
  • UPF50 fabric blocks harmful UV rays, provides excellent protection against sunburn.
  • Durable water repellent finish to repel light rain and stains.

Product Details

  • Partial Elastic Waist- can be adjusted according to waist circumference.
  • 4 Deep Pockets- secure store your valuable items.
  • Back Zipper Pockets- suitable for your card or keys.
  • D-Ring with Small Pocket- allows for easy hooking up of hiking gear.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

janeo
4.0 out of 5 stars Handsome, Well Appointed Lightweight Cargo-Style Shorts
Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
Size: 32Color: Light KhakiVerified Purchase
My son needed "khaki-type" shorts for regulation use on his youth bowling team. I spied these on AMAZON, read the reviews, and decided to give these a try.

These are indeed, lightweight. They have a fine graph-like texture to the fabric, but it is hardly noticeable. The color purchased was LIGHT KHAKI, however they are NOT as light in color as I thought they might be. The pockets are plentiful, including fairly deep ones on each side and a tiny coin pocket on the upper right. The zippered pockets (3) are useful and seem to feature quality zippers with a sturdy elastic/rubber pull. In my opinion, these shorts fit true-to-size or maybe just a bit on the smaller end. The legs fall just above my son's knee, and provide just enough stretch to allow him comfort during bowling. They also feature a nice elastic band at each side of the waist which again, accommodates some athleticism. They wash up nicely, and when hung immediately from the dryer, have little to no wrinkles. The only caveat I can see is perhaps a tendency to be a bit unforgiving (taught) in the crotch, which may in part be due to the flat front style, however this minor issue may be dependent on the overall "size" of your guy. (When sporting these shorts, my son will forego his usual boxer brief in lieu of a more form fitting brief to allow more support/discretion.)

While definitely NOT a cheap version of lightweight shorts, my son and I are relatively pleased with this purchase.
